node.text:
This amazing collaborative animation between @c_bass3d and @neoporkog beautifully captures with amazing sights we will see when Starship leaves Earth for the first time!

You can watch the full YouTube video here:
https://youtu.be/iFt_LsFRFEQ
⚠️it's 8 minutes of pure awesomeness⚠️
.
.
Follow @neoporkog and @c_bass3d on here aswell as twitter for more amazing work!
.
.

.
